creator: SWAR Doctor LLC
descriptionHtml:
SWAR Doctor LLC has developed this easy and safe application to help people manage/ storage their own health records prescription, lab report, doctor report, child vaccination, maternity and COVID records. We are part of Microsoft Partner Network, hence using Microsoft Azure cloud storage which is accessible worldwide 24X7.

CHAT FEATURES: Besides health record management, you can securely voice call, video call, chat with friends/family, also post your health status or comments in activity feeds.

SECURITY ENABLED:  SWAR Doctor LLC with its research and development team has built the application using end-to-end encryption which ensures complete data privacy. SWAR application and websites offer safe and secure storage for your healthcare needs.

EASY to USE: You can either take pictures of your healthcare document or simply attach files and upload to SWAR Doctor App in 2 steps. Also, our unique/uniform folder structure and storage system for all stake holders (common people to all doctors & healthcare service providers) is a transformation in healthcare sector.

UNIQUE & FIRST OF THE KIND: Neither government nor private sector healthcare providers can manage your health record. ONLY YOU CAN, with the help of SWAR Doctor. Individual users can access the security enabled (OTP based) personal health record from worldwide using web browsers or mobile applications, compatible with iOS and Android.

IN PROGRESS: SWAR Doctor LLC is developing a state-of-the art Internet platform integrating all healthcare stakeholders including users, doctors, healthcare specialist like therapist, counselors, pharmacies, laboratories etc.

UPCOMING FEATURES: Chat with Doctors and Specialists, book appointments, online consultations, home visit doctors/ nurses, order medicine from nearby retail pharmacies, clinic software. Doctors and healthcare specialists can build their own profile and patient base demonstrating their own performance

SWAR Doctor cares for YOU, offering a cost-effective solution to clinics, multi-users, with multi-level safe interactive interfaces through SWAR Clinic Management System.
descriptionShort: SWAR Doctor App is a safe & secure design for seamless healthcare experience
